OL,3,C'It made me cry': Viral photos of
OL,4,CSwiss glacier show impact of climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FPhotos of a couple posing in the same
OL,8,Fspot of the Swiss Alps 15 years apart
OL,9,Fhave gone viral, after they showed the
OL,10,Fdevastating impact of climate change
OL,11,Fand the speed at which glaciers are
OL,12,Fmelting.
OL,14,FDuncan Porter and his wife Helen
OL,15,Fposted the photos on X and attracted
OL,16,Fthe attention of millions of people,
OL,17,Fsparking both heartbreak and criticism
OL,18,Ffrom users.
