OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe photos show the British couple
OL,8,Fposing in front of the same spot of
OL,9,Fthe Rhone glacier in August 2009 and
OL,10,FAugust 2024.
OL,12,FIn the photo from 2009, the ice
OL,13,Fcompletely fills the background.
OL,14,FHowever, in 2024, the white ice has
OL,15,Fvisibly melted, and in its place is a
OL,16,Fgrey rock and a lake.
OL,18,FPosting on X, Porter said: "Fifteen
OL,19,Fyears minus one day between these
OL,20,Fphotos. Taken at the Rhone glacier in
OL,21,FSwitzerland today.
