OL,7,F"Not gonna lie, it made me cry."
OL,9,FPorter and his wife returned to the
OL,10,Fspot with their teenage daughters,
OL,11,FMaisie and Emily, in a hope to
OL,12,Frecreate the photo.
OL,14,F"But obviously the circumstance of
OL,15,Fthis photo was drastically different,"
OL,16,FPorter told the Guardian.
OL,18,FHelen Porter said: "I thought it was
OL,19,Freally unbelievable."
