OL,12,FSwitzerland is home to the most
OL,13,Fglaciers of any country in Europe.
OL,15,FHowever, in two years, 10% of the
OL,16,Fcountry's glaciers ice volume has
OL,17,Fdisappeared as a result of low
OL,18,Fsnowfall and rising temperatures,
OL,19,Faccording to data from the Swiss
OL,20,FAcademy of Sciences.
