OL,3,C'It made me cry': Viral photos of
OL,4,CSwiss glacier show impact of climate
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FIn 2022, the total glacier volume
OL,8,Fdecreased by 6% - the biggest decrease
OL,9,Fsince measurements began. This was
OL,10,Fclosely followed by 2023 which had a
OL,11,F4% drop, the figures show.
OL,13,FThe reduction over the last two years
OL,14,Fwas the same as what was lost in the
OL,15,Fperiod between 1960 and 1990, the
OL,16,FSwiss Academy of Sciences said.
OL,18,FMany users on X reacted in shock to
OL,19,Fthe visible change in the glacier,
OL,20,Fwith the post being viewed 4.2 million
OL,21,Ftimes as of Tuesday.
